{{Infobox cricket ground|ground_name=Tehmas Khan Football Stadium|image=|caption=Tehmas Khan Football Stadium|country=Pakistan|location=[[Shahi Bagh]], [[Peshawar]]|establishment=|seating_capacity=6 000|owner=|operator=District Government Peshawar|tenants=}}

'''Tehmas Khan Football Stadium''' also spell as Tamas Khan Football Ground is a historical football ground located at [[Faqeerabad, Peshawar|Faqirabad Peshawar]], the capital of [[Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]] province of [[Pakistan]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/632759|title=Govt to double allocation for sports|last=Newspaper|first=From the|date=2011-05-29|work=DAWN.COM|access-date=2018-11-12|language=en-US}}</ref>

== Overview ==
Tehmas Khan Football stadium is located in the vicinity of historical [[Shahi Bagh|Shahi Bagh Peshawar]] adjacent to [[Arbab Niaz Stadium|Arbab Niaz Cricket Stadium]] and [[Peshawar Gymkhana Ground]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/767183/the-shahi-bagh/|title=The Shahi Bagh {{!}} The Express Tribune|date=2014-09-25|work=The Express Tribune|access-date=2018-11-12|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://nation.com.pk/18-Jan-2016/rulers-plundered-national-exchequer-siraj|title=Rulers plundered national exchequer: Siraj|date=2016-01-18|work=The Nation|access-date=2018-11-12|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/12632-anp-chief-warns-against-changing-corridor-route|title=ANP chief warns against changing corridor route|access-date=2018-11-12|language=en}}</ref> It is very popular among club footballers and football tournaments are regularly played here.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://fp.brecorder.com/2018/11/20181109422441/|title=NBP KP Inter-District Soccer: Charsadda, Peshawar Red advance to next round {{!}} Business Recorder|date=2018-11-09|work=Business Recorder|access-date=2018-11-12|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.urdupoint.com/en/sports/charsadda-stun-peshawar-white-in-13th-kp-nbp-477079.html|title=Charsadda Stun Peshawar White In 13th KP NBP Inter-District Football - UrduPoint|work=UrduPoint|access-date=2018-11-12|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pakistanpoint.com/en/story/477732/peshawar-red-enters-into-semi-final-in-13th-nbp-inter-d.html|title=Peshawar Red Enters Into Semi-final In 13th NBP Inter-District Soccer|last=|first=|date=|website=www.pakistanpoint.com|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-11-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.app.com.pk/13th-nbp-khyber-pakhtunkhwa-inter-district-men-football-from-nov-5/|title=13th NBP Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Inter-District Men Football from Nov 5|date=2018-10-29|work=Associated Press Of Pakistan|access-date=2018-11-12|language=en-US}}</ref> The stadium currently has the seating capacity of 6000.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pakistaninsiders.wordpress.com/category/asia/page/162/|title=Asia {{!}} Pakistan Insider {{!}} Page 162|website=pakistaninsiders.wordpress.com|language=en|access-date=2018-11-12}}</ref> 

